data.name: textBox3.Text
data.value: Hello, I am Omar Faruk. I am a cleaner at a local school. Currently I had an accident and I lost one of my legs. I am going to have a surgery and do the treatments to add an artificial leg. For that, I need a lot of money. I have managed half of the money. I need help for the rest worth 3000 dollars. I have attached my medical reports and bills fyi.

data.name: textBox5.Text
data.value: In a small town, a local community center was devastated by a fire. Among those affected is Sarah, a young girl who tragically lost both of her parents. Her grandparents, struggling to support her, need $5,000 for her education and well-being. Your donation of $3,000 would make a significant impact, helping Sarah rebuild her life and pursue her dreams of becoming a doctor. Please consider supporting Sarah and giving her a chance for a brighter future.
